name: animeElves
description:
This mix is based on my realisticElves model, which was not able to consistently produce anime, so I went back into my model archive and dug out several anime models and made this animeElves model. It obviously can make animes elves, but it also can do landscapes, spaceships, aliens, chibi anime, cats, shibas and alot more. Its very difficult to push back into realism, but not impossible.

As with realisticElves I sugest you get the standard vae for SD1.5, or the output will not be consistent. Also like realisticElves, lewd content is possible, but it is not designed for it. Viewer discretion advised.
